CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 15, 1954, pg. 19, reads: "'United Nations' Team - Chuck Fly, dancer extraordinary, is doing a great job as member of this group being billed as a 'United Nations' Dance Team at the Horizon Room at the Greater Pittsburgh Airport. Left to right: Chuck Fly, Vince Carson, Coco Cartier and Ching. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: "United Nations" dance team members Chuck Fly, Vince Carson, Coco Cartier, and Ching posed in interior with leaf patterned carpeting
